This directory contains the source files of Jigloo, a translator from
Java to Bigloo. Cigloo scans JVM class files and produces Bigloo
Java clauses.

In order to compile Jigloo, you need a standard Java compiler. To
compile Cigloo just enter `make'.

To install Jigloo just enter `make install'. 

To check Jigloo options, enter `java jigloo -help'.

	
